metadata.name: TikTok Activist Donald 01
metadata.description:
TikTok activism is a collection of 49 tokens, the collection comprised entirely of unique one-of-one NFTs. 
 The collection feature 5 original characters created only for the first release of nss NFTs.
 Every minted asset in this open edition comes with nss’ report about “The power of TikTok”
 This token is a collectible that lives on the Ethereum blockchain.
